      // About Us
      "aboutUs.title": "About Us",
      "aboutUs.intro": "XIAOXIONG Market is an exploration platform that interweaves History, Architecture, and Dining.\nHere,\nevery restaurant is a trace left by time;\nevery building carries the memory of a city.\nWe care not only about flavors, but also about the architectural lineage and cultural memory behind each restaurant.\nThe platform gathers historically significant restaurants and architectural spaces from around the world, and encourages users to share their own discoveries — so that the overlooked restaurants and stories around us can be seen again, turning dining from mere consumption into a journey of understanding and discovery.\nWe seek to understand how cities grow through the wisdom of the East, interpreting the transformation and continuity of spaces through the lens of the I Ching, so that the stories of time and space can be understood anew.\nFood, architecture, history — they have always been there.\nXiaoxiong Market simply helps you see them.",
